603
00:37:40,347 --> 00:37:41,866
Here, look at my hair.

604
00:37:41,867 --> 00:37:42,706
Feel it.

605
00:37:42,707 --> 00:37:44,386
Do I have hair fall?

606
00:37:44,387 --> 00:37:46,798
- Then why is she losing her hair?
