607
00:37:48,548 --> 00:37:49,997
Are these what you bought?

608
00:37:50,787 --> 00:37:52,346
Did you use this to dye her hair?

609
00:37:52,347 --> 00:37:53,758
Go and check.

610
00:37:53,827 --> 00:37:54,627
What should I check?

611
00:37:54,628 --> 00:37:56,027
