624
00:38:22,267 --> 00:38:23,947
Xiang Zhijun, listen.

625
00:38:23,948 --> 00:38:26,637
Think about it yourself.

626
00:38:26,707 --> 00:38:27,838
Use your brain.

627
00:38:27,908 --> 00:38:30,637
