to get it checked out.

628
00:38:30,667 --> 00:38:31,987
Don't be stingy this time.

629
00:38:31,988 --> 00:38:33,346
Go to a large-scale hospital. Understand?

630
00:38:33,347 --> 00:38:33,947
You go yourself.

631
00:38:33,948 --> 00:38:34,507
You go.

632
00:38:34,508 --> 00:38:35,507
You go.

633
00:38:35,508 --> 00:38:36,346
