658
00:39:29,347 --> 00:39:31,358
It's just time.

659
00:39:32,307 --> 00:39:33,398
It's fine.

660
00:39:33,588 --> 00:39:35,278
Stop overthink.

661
00:39:35,387 --> 00:39:38,077
What are you talking about?

662
00:39:42,988 --> 00:39:45,306
It's fine. Don't worry.

663
00:39:45,307 --> 00:39:47,477
I'm here, don't be afraid.

664
00:39:48,267 --> 00:39:49,798
Nothing will happen.

665
00:39:53,468 --> 00:39:54,306
I'm not afraid.

666
00:39:54,307 --> 00:39:56,037
I'm just worried about you.

667
00:39:58,588 --> 00:39:59,838
I'll be fine if you are.

668
00:40:00,028 --> 00:40:01,437
